node.text: Today, I want to highlight the importance of voter protection at the polls. @wetheactionorg is deploying lawyers to polling places across the country to ensure our votes are protected. I have many wonderful lawyers in my life who have already volunteered their time to protect our votes. If you’re a lawyer or know a lawyer, please sign up for or share We The Action!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Lady Gaga on July 19, 2021. May be a black-and-white image of one or more people and text that says 'ONE LAST TIME AN EVENING WITH TONY BENNETT & LADY GAGA AUGUST 3RD & 5TH RADIO CITY'.

node.text: One Last Time 🤍 An evening with @itstonybennett and me at Radio City Music Hall on August 3rd & 5th. I am so honored and excited to celebrate Tony’s 95th birthday with him at these special shows. Tickets go on sale Thursday, July 22nd at 10am ET on livenation.com ✨

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Lady Gaga on July 15, 2021. May be a closeup of 1 person.

node.text: I can’t believe my makeup brand is 2 years old this week. Thank you so much to my team @hauslabs for celebrating all people,  beauty that is boundary less, reminding us all there is an artist inside us— and for working so hard this last two years.  We can’t wait to show you the future…🖤
